            "name": "Sara Levi-Tanai",
            "bio": "Sara Levi-Tanai (Hebrew: שרה לוי-תנאי‎‎; c. 1910 – 3 October 2005) was an Israeli choreographer and song writer. She was the founder and artistic director of the Inbal Dance Theater and recipient of the Israel Prize in dance in 1973.",
